NVM is a version manager for Node.js.

**NOTE:** The [github repository](https://github.com/creationix/nvm) provides installation instructions.  If you install this with homebrew, things are likely to break!

~~~bash
$ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.31.7/install.sh | bash
$ source .bashrc
$ nvm install v6.2.0
$ nvm alias default v6.2.0
~~~